## Telegram IDs — Roles

| Role | Telegram ID | Description |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| **<operator_name> (admin/dev)** | `<your_admin_chat_id>` | Project owner. Receives technical alerts, errors, and system health notifications. Does NOT receive business reports. |
| **<intermediary_name> (beta)** | `<your_intermediary_chat_id>` | Intermediate tester. Also receives operational business notifications. |
| **<client_name>** | `<your_client_chat_id>` | End client. Primary recipient of business reports, stock alerts, SEO suggestions, and all operational communication. |

### Routing rules

- **Technical errors and system health** → <operator_name> (`<your_admin_chat_id>`)
- **Business reports, stock alerts, SEO, suggestions** → <intermediary_name> (`<your_intermediary_chat_id>`) and <client_name> (`<your_client_chat_id>`)
- **Testing/development** → <intermediary_name> (`<your_intermediary_chat_id>`)
